org.liris.ktbs.dao.rest
Interface KtbsRestClient

All Known Implementing Classes:
ApacheKtbsRestClient
public interface KtbsRestClient

A RDF-level interface to a KTBS server through the REST API. Instances of this interface must handle the HTTP communication with the remote KTBS.

This interface is said to be RDF-level because it does not handle Java representation of KTBS resources, but instead the RDF representation defined by the KTBS Server API.

Author:
Damien Cram
